---

## Verification Checklist

- [ ] Review all breaking changes listed above
- [ ] Run auto-migration: `ggen diff migrate --auto`
- [ ] Verify generated code compiles: `cargo build` / `go build` / `mix compile`
- [ ] Run test suite: `cargo test` / `go test` / `mix test`
- [ ] Verify no deprecated types remain in generated code
- [ ] Update downstream consumers of changed types
- [ ] Run verification SPARQL queries for each auto-migrated change

---

## How to Use This Report

1. **Review breaking changes** — these require manual intervention before upgrade
2. **Apply auto-migrations** — run `ggen diff migrate --auto` for safe changes
3. **Verify compilation** — ensure generated code still compiles after migration
4. **Run tests** — full test suite must pass after migration
5. **Update consumers** — notify downstream projects of API changes

### Change Types

| Type | Description | Breaking? |
|------|-------------|-----------|
| **added** | New entity or property added | No |
| **removed** | Entity or property removed | Yes |
| **modified** | Type or range changed | Maybe |
| **renamed** | Entity or property renamed | Yes |
| **deprecated** | Marked for future removal | No (yet) |
| **cardinality_change** | Min/max cardinality changed | Maybe |

